line.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <h3 class=\"ttl\">\n              <strong class=\"font-jp-min color-wh\">新卒採用<span>（27年度卒業）</span></strong>\n              <small class=\"font-en color-gre\">Entry For Graduate Recruitment</small>\n            </h3>\n            <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/mynav.png\" height=\"59\" width=\"71\" alt=\"新卒応募 マイナビ\"></i>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"gnav--parent\">\n          <a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/28/pc/search/corp73236/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <h3 class=\"ttl\">\n              <strong class=\"font-jp-min color-wh\">新卒採用<span>（28年度卒業）</span></strong>\n              <small class=\"font-en color-gre\">Entry For Graduate Recruitment</small>\n            </h3>\n            <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/mynav.png\" height=\"59\" width=\"71\" alt=\"新卒応募 マイナビ\"></i>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"gnav--parent\">\n          <a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/mincareer/\">\n            <h3 class=\"ttl\">\n              <strong class=\"font-jp-min color-wh\">中途採用</strong>\n              <small class=\"font-en color-gre\">Entry For Career Recruitment</small>\n            </h3>\n            <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/mail.png\" height=\"48\" width=\"64\" alt=\"中途応募\"></i>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n    <hr>\n    <h1 class=\"header--logo\">\n      <a href=\"/recruitment/\">\n        <small>株式会社市川工務店 リクルートサイト</small>\n        <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/common/head_logo.png\" alt=\"㈱市川工務店｜求人・採用サイト｜岐阜県で土木・建築技術者へ\" width=\"140\" height=\"44\">\n      </a>\n    </h1>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"entry_btn sp-none\">\n      <a href=\"#entry\" class=\"font-jp-min smooth\"><span class=\"font-en\">Entry</span>応募する</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  \n<main>\n\n  <!-- start hero -->\n  <section class=\"hero\" id=\"hero\">\n    <div class=\"hero--visual\">\n      <h2 class=\"hero--ttl flex flex-j-between\">\n        <span class=\"waypoint fade\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/hero_catch3.png\" height=\"245\" width=\"39\" alt=\"市川工務店。\"></span>\n        <span class=\"waypoint fade\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/hero_catch2.png\" height=\"188\" width=\"35\" alt=\"イチから。\"></span>\n        <span class=\"waypoint fade\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/hero_catch1.png\" height=\"190\" width=\"39\" alt=\"暮らしを、\"></span>\n      </h2>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <!-- end hero -->\n\n  <!-- start home_about -->\n  <section class=\"section_pdg-sm home_about bg-pt1\" id=\"home_about\">\n    <div class=\"inner-xl\">\n      <ul class=\"home_about--gallery waypoint flex flex-sp-block fade flex-j-between\" id=\"home_about--gallery\">\n        <li>\n          <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery1.png\" height=\"885\" width=\"859\" alt=\"長良川うかいミュージアム／十六銀行加納支店／小島山トンネル\" class=\"sp-none-inline\">\n          <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery1_sp.png\" alt=\"汗出せ、知恵出せ、まじめに働け。\" width=\"226\" height=\"156\" class=\"pc-none-inline\">\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery2.png\" alt=\"汗出せ、知恵出せ、まじめに働け。／瞑想の森\" width=\"503\" height=\"885\" class=\"sp-none-inline\">\n          <div class=\"home_about_slide pc-none\">\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery2-1_sp.jpg\" alt=\"瞑想の森\"></div>\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery2-2_sp.jpg\" alt=\"東海環状自動車道\"></div>\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery2-3_sp.jpg\" alt=\"十六銀行加納支店\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery3.png\" alt=\"東海環状自動車道／鵜飼い大橋\" width=\"494\" height=\"885\" class=\"sp-none-inline\">\n          <div class=\"home_about_slide pc-none\">\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery3-1_sp.jpg\" alt=\"長良川うかいミュージアム\"></div>\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery3-2_sp.jpg\" alt=\"小島山トンネル\"></div>\n            <div><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/home_about_gallery3-3_sp.jpg\" alt=\"鵜飼い大橋\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"home_about--newvalue waypoint fade flex flex-sp-block flex-j-between\" id=\"home_about--newvalue\">\n        <div class=\"txtarea\">\n          <h2 class=\"heading-1 mgn-btm32\">それが私たちの社訓。<br>でも、これからの時代、<br>私たちで変えていくんだ。</h2>\n          <p class=\"mgn-btm16\">工務という言葉は、「土木や建築に関する仕事」を意味する。<br class=\"sp-none\">市川工務店は、まさにその名のとおり道路・橋脚・河川・下水道といった土木・舗装工事と、公共施設や教育・医療施設、博物館や美術館などの建築工事から店舗・住宅のリフォーム工事まで、幅広く事業を展開している。1950年の設立から、ずっと岐阜県内の街の発展に携わってきた土木と建築のプロフェッショナルだ。</p>\n          <p class=\"mgn-btm16\">さあ、新しい時代。</p>\n          <p class=\"mgn-btm16\">街は変わる。人は変わる。価値は変わる。暮らしが変わる。<br class=\"sp-none\">私たちも変わろう、変えていこう。</p>\n          <p>土木・建築業界のイメージをひっくりかえすほどの、<br class=\"sp-none\">新しい時代の働きやすさを、市川工務店に。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"imgarea\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <!-- end home_about -->\n  <section class=\"section_pdg home_movie bg-pt1\" id=\"home_movie\">\n    <div class=\"home_movie--content inner waypoint fade\">\n      <h2 class=\"heading-1 txt-ctr txt-sp-lft mgn-btm24\">5分でわかる、<br class=\"pc-none\">市川工務店。</h2>\n      <div class=\"youtube--wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"youtube\">\n          <iframe width=\"1080\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WPDuixRBUQ0?loop=1&playlist=WPDuixRBUQ0\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <!-- start home_welfare -->\n  <section class=\"section_pdg home_welfare bg-pt1\" id=\"home_welfare\">\n    <div class=\"home_welfare--content inner inner-lg waypoint fade\">\n      <h2 class=\"heading-1 txt-ctr txt-sp-lft mgn-btm24\">働きやすい。<br class=\"pc-none\">市川工務店。</h2>\n      <p class=\"txt-ctr txt-sp-lft mgn-btm40\">市川工務店は「働きやすさの追求」に取り組んでおり、<br>さまざまな企業認定を受けています。</p>\n      <ul class=\"home_welfare--content--list flex flex-col4 flex-j-ctr flex-sp-block mgn-btm40\">\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img2.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"厚生労働省くるみん\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>令和３年に３度目、<br class=\"sp-none\">岐阜県内事業者の０.１％のみ</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">子育てサポート企業<br>（くるみん）認定<br>（平成23年初回認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img5.png\" height=\"311\" width=\"377\" alt=\"健康経営優良法人\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>経産省が制度設計した審査を経て、全国の中小企業の平均0.7％だけが認定</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">日本健康会議<br>健康経営優良法人<br>（平成31年より毎年認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img1.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"岐阜県ワーク・ライフ・バランス推進エクセレント企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>岐阜県による審査を経て、対象企業が拡大された初年度での認定</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">岐阜県ワーク・ライフ・バランス推進エクセレント企業（平成27年認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img8.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"ぎふ建設人材育成リーディング企業ゴールドランク\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>制度開始初年度に<br class=\"sp-none\">最高ランクに認定</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">ぎふ建設人材育成<br>リーディング企業<br>ゴールドランク<br>（平成29年度初回認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img9.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"子育て支援企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>表彰制度開始初年度に認定、<br class=\"sp-none\">建設業では唯一</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">岐阜県<br>清流の国ぎふ健康経営優良企業2020<br>（令和2年受賞）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img3.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"岐阜市男女共同参画\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>世の中に先駆けて、<br>10年以上前から<br>女性活躍を推進</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">岐阜市男女共同参画<br>優良事業者表彰受賞<br>（平成21年受賞）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img10.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"子育て支援企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>制度開始初年度に認定</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">岐阜市<br>ぎふし共育・女性活躍企業<br>（令和2年受賞）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img6.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"ファミリーフレンドリー企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>本社のある<br>岐阜県だけではなく<br>支社単位で<br>愛知県から認定</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">愛知県<br>ファミリーフレンドリー<br>企業（平成28年認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img11.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"子育て支援企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>名古屋支社で認証取得</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">愛知県<br>あいち女性輝きカンパニー<br>（平成29年度）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img7.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"子育て支援企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>名古屋市の<br>事業者12万のうち、<br>196社のみ認定<br><small>（令和4年4月1日現在）</small></h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">名古屋市<br>子育て支援企業<br>（平成21年認定）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <i><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/welfare_img12.jpg\" height=\"149\" width=\"185\" alt=\"子育て支援企業\"></i>\n          <div class=\"txt\">\n            <h3>名古屋支社で認証取得、<br class=\"sp-none\">180社のみ認証<br><small>（令和2年2月12日現在）</small></h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-xs\">名古屋市<br>ワーク・ライフ・バランス推進企業<br>（令和元年度）</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"txt-ctr\"><a href=\"/recruitment/welfare/\" class=\"btn\">働きやすさを知る</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"inner-xl\">\n      <ul class=\"home_welfare--gallery sp-none-flex flex-j-between\">\n        <li class=\"gallery1\"></li>\n        <li class=\"gallery2\"></li>\n        <li class=\"gallery3\"></li>\n        <li class=\"gallery4\"></li>\n      </ul>\n      <hr class=\"section_hr pc-none\">\n      <hr class=\"section_hr pc-none\">\n      <hr class=\"section_hr pc-none\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <!-- end home_welfare -->\n\n  <!-- start home_work -->\n  <section class=\"home_work\" id=\"home_work\">\n    <div class=\"inner-xl mgn-btm56 sp-none\" id=\"home_work--intro\">\n      <hr class=\"section_hr\">\n      <hr class=\"section_hr\">\n      <hr class=\"section_hr mgn-btm80\">\n      <h2 class=\"section_ttl waypoint fade\">\n        <strong>私たちの仕事</strong>\n        <small class=\"color-bro\">Ichikawa’s Cool Works</small>\n      </h2>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"home_work--content\">\n      <li class=\"col col-1 flex flex-reverse flex-sp-block waypoint fade\" id=\"home_work--col1\">\n        <div class=\"txtarea\">\n          <h2 class=\"section_ttl pc-none\">\n            <strong>私たちの仕事</strong>\n            <small class=\"color-bro\">Ichikawa’s Cool Works</small>\n          </h2>\n          <div class=\"txtarea--inner\">\n            <span class=\"num\">\n              <small><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/txt_works.png\" height=\"8\" width=\"36\" alt=\"WORKS\"></small>\n              <strong class=\"font-num\">01</strong>\n              <strong class=\"font-en color-gre\">Civil Engineering</strong>\n            </span>\n            <h3 class=\"heading-1 mgn-btm40\">土木で、<br>街をつくって。</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-sm mgn-btm40\">高速道路・国道・県道などの道路工事、河川工事、トンネル工事、ダム工事などの土木工事・道路の舗装工事など、地域になくてはならない社会インフラを支えています。</p>\n            <p><a href=\"/recruitment/business/#public_section\" class=\"btn\">土木事業について知る</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"imgarea\"></div>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"col col-2 flex flex-sp-block waypoint fade\" id=\"home_work--col2\">\n        <div class=\"txtarea\">\n          <div class=\"txtarea--inner\">\n            <span class=\"num font-jp-min\">\n              <small><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/txt_works.png\" height=\"8\" width=\"36\" alt=\"WORKS\"></small>\n              <strong class=\"font-num\">02</strong>\n              <strong class=\"font-en color-gre\">Architecture</strong>\n            </span>\n            <h3 class=\"heading-1 mgn-btm40\">建築で、<br>暮らしを豊かに。</h3>\n            <p class=\"txt-sm mgn-btm64\">公共施設のほか、地元企業の工場や倉庫、事務所・店舗などの建築工事で地域のみなさんの暮らしを支えています。また企業の事務所や工場以外にも、住宅のリフォーム工事も対応します。</p>\n            <p><a href=\"/recruitment/business/#architecture_section\" class=\"btn\">建築事業について知る</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"imgarea\"></div>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n  <!-- end home_work -->\n\n  <!-- start home_recruit -->\n  <section class=\"section_pdg home_recruit bg-pt1\" id=\"home_recruit\">\n    <h2 class=\"section_ttl txt-ctr inner waypoint fade mgn-btm56\" id=\"home_recruit--intro\">\n      <strong>募集職種</strong>\n      <small class=\"color-gre\">Job Category</small>\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"home_recruit--list waypoint fade\" id=\"home_recruit--list\">\n      <article class=\"recruit_post civil\">\n        <div class=\"recruit_post--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"heading-2 mgn-btm24 color-wh\">人々の生活を<br>支え、災害を<br>未然に防ぐ。</h3>\n          <p class=\"job mgn-btm24\"><span>土木技術者（施工管理）</span></p>\n          <p class=\"link\"><a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/graduate/p357/\" class=\"btn-en color-gre\">Detail</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"recruit_post building\">\n        <div class=\"recruit_post--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"heading-2 mgn-btm24 color-wh\">名前すらない土地を、<br>地図に残し、<br>人の集う場所へ。</h3>\n          <p class=\"job mgn-btm24\"><span>建築技術者（施工管理）</span></p>\n          <p class=\"link\"><a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/graduate/p425/\" class=\"btn-en color-gre\">Detail</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"recruit_post civil\">\n        <div class=\"recruit_post--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"heading-2 mgn-btm24 color-wh\">CADで引いた、<br>ひとすじの線が<br>街の一部になって動き出す。</h3>\n          <p class=\"job mgn-btm24\"><span>土木技術者（調査設計）</span></p>\n          <p class=\"link\"><a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/graduate/p424/\" class=\"btn-en color-gre\">Detail</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"recruit_post sales\">\n        <div class=\"recruit_post--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"heading-2 mgn-btm24 color-wh\">携わった仕事が、<br>岐阜をもっと<br>輝かせる楽しみ。</h3>\n          <p class=\"job mgn-btm24\"><span>営業</span></p>\n          <p class=\"link\"><a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/graduate/p426/\" class=\"btn-en color-gre\">Detail</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"recruit_post office\">\n        <div class=\"recruit_post--inner\">\n          <h3 class=\"heading-2 mgn-btm24 color-wh\">現場の仕事を、<br>縁の下から、<br>やさしく支える。</h3>\n          <p class=\"job mgn-btm24\"><span>事務</span></p>\n          <p class=\"link\"><a href=\"/recruitment/requirements/graduate/p427/\" class=\"btn-en color-gre\">Detail</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <!-- end home_recruit -->\n\n  <!-- start home_interview -->\r\n<section class=\"section_pdg home_interview bg-pt1\" id=\"home_interview\">\r\n  <div class=\"inner waypoint fade\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"section_ttl mgn-btm64\">\r\n      <strong>先輩たちの声</strong>\r\n      <small class=\"color-bro\">Senior Interview</small>\r\n    </h2>\r\n    <div id=\"interview_slide\" class=\"interview--list mgn-btm64\">\r\n                <article class=\"interview_col\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://www.ic-group.co.jp/recruitment/interview/p475/\">\r\n    <div class=\"interview_img\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/7d6791cd63d5fb3eee968a96b3307bc3.jpg);\">\r\n      <div class=\"hover sp-none\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/c3a80ec995b7d35b433e3d6b7485290e.jpg);\"></div>\r\n      <div class=\"hover pc-none\" style=\"background-image:url();\"></div>\r\n      <span class=\"num\">\r\n        <small class=\"mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/txt_interview.png\" height=\"6\" width=\"44\" alt=\"INTERVIEW\"></small>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-num\">01</strong>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-en\">D.T</strong>\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h3 class=\"interview_name\">\r\n      <small>営業職</small>      <strong class=\"font-jp-min\">D.T</strong>\r\n    </h3>\r\n  </a>\r\n</article>            <article class=\"interview_col\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://www.ic-group.co.jp/recruitment/interview/p461/\">\r\n    <div class=\"interview_img\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/02695d0978865945393f40bebf70f51c.jpg);\">\r\n      <div class=\"hover sp-none\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/df08b675df05232c730019b7772c19ec.jpg);\"></div>\r\n      <div class=\"hover pc-none\" style=\"background-image:url();\"></div>\r\n      <span class=\"num\">\r\n        <small class=\"mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/txt_interview.png\" height=\"6\" width=\"44\" alt=\"INTERVIEW\"></small>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-num\">02</strong>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-en\">T.T</strong>\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h3 class=\"interview_name\">\r\n      <small>施工管理</small>      <strong class=\"font-jp-min\">T.T</strong>\r\n    </h3>\r\n  </a>\r\n</article>            <article class=\"interview_col\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://www.ic-group.co.jp/recruitment/interview/p375/\">\r\n    <div class=\"interview_img\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/b391f648242aee7846bcd071183d21e8.jpg);\">\r\n      <div class=\"hover sp-none\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bdef1380525f8889d94d306d2c02dc71.jpg);\"></div>\r\n      <div class=\"hover pc-none\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/e1ad11d95b7d921867fc189bd82cc288-856x443.jpg);\"></div>\r\n      <span class=\"num\">\r\n        <small class=\"mgn-btm8\"><img src=\"/recruitment/wp/wp-content/themes/original_theme/images/txt_interview.png\" height=\"6\" width=\"44\" alt=\"INTERVIEW\"></small>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-num\">03</strong>\r\n        <strong class=\"font-en\">T.I</strong>\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h3 class=\"interview_name\">\r\n      <small>建築技術者（施工管理）</small>      <strong class=\"font-jp-min\">T.I</strong>\r\n    </h3>\r\n  </a>\r\n</article>            <article class=\"interview_col\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://www.ic-group.co.jp/recruitment/interview/p499/\">\r\n    <div class=\"interview_img\" style=\"background-image:url(/recruitment/wp/wp-co